{"tid":467366,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[不服找連9投訴]近年十大遠射高手","createTime":"2017-11-13T12:29:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T14:51:32.000Z","uid":20032,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b8ecc16c278cb179c32bb3a65da494d10876529f","tid":467366,"uid":20032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T12:29:28.000Z","msg":"10. 克雷&middot;湯普森<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static2.businessinsider.com/image/575f6e709105842b008c8b74-891/klay%20thompson%203.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic2.businessinsider.com%2Fimage%2F575f6e709105842b008c8b74-891%2Fklay%2520thompson%25203.jpg&h=63849a69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n克雷&middot;湯普森是聯盟最頂級的得分後衛，能攻能守，三分球是他的一大利器，常常瞬間致敵人於死地。雖然他的出手尚算合理，但在三分球遠射的領域上，絕對不容忽視，可惜不夠以下的球員癲。<br />\n<br />\n9.羅素&middot;韋斯布魯克<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-e4JRhj2jf4M/WQbs7mtEtnI/AAAAAAAAMmQ/Pzjel-gbQLAHGIxBuKcs3M5x6HmHt5fNwCLcB/s1600/mvpruss_2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-e4JRhj2jf4M%2FWQbs7mtEtnI%2FAAAAAAAAMmQ%2FPzjel-gbQLAHGIxBuKcs3M5x6HmHt5fNwCLcB%2Fs1600%2Fmvpruss_2.gif&h=178a01f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n威少是全聯盟最全能的控球後衛，得分籃板一把罩，完全不給敵人和隊友發揮的空間，雖然三分球我也不知道他有什麼厲害的地方，但fans很多而且highlight 看起來很猛，就給他個第9吧！<br />\n<br />\n7.以賽亞&middot;湯馬士<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images0.minutemediacdn.com/production/912x516/58f4008c86f2f58c9c000001.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages0.minutemediacdn.com%2Fproduction%2F912x516%2F58f4008c86f2f58c9c000001.png&h=5b92f322&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被街場譽為mini IT 的我也無法避免地關注這位球星，上賽季他擔任球隊進攻大旗甚至一度被認為是MVP 的候選人，一手鬼神莫測的切入配合超遠程三分，令人防不勝防！"},{"pid":"80b9c748c3dc10fe4ab5e2c172d196fe80a9d987","tid":467366,"uid":20032,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T12:40:48.000Z","msg":"6. 麥克&middot;康利<br />\n<img src=\"https://d3d2maoophos6y.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/22180935/Screen-Shot-2017-04-22-at-9.08.27-PM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd3d2maoophos6y.cloudfront.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2F22180935%2FScreen-Shot-2017-04-22-at-9.08.27-PM.png&h=498f1b18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾經是聯盟最貴的他，似乎跟三分高手無關，但其實遠程三分很厲害！誰看誰知道！<br />\n<br />\n5. 高比&middot;拜仁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.gettyimages.com/photos/kobe-bryant-of-the-los-angeles-lakers-shoots-over-dwyane-wade-of-the-picture-id93979797\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.gettyimages.com%2Fphotos%2Fkobe-bryant-of-the-los-angeles-lakers-shoots-over-dwyane-wade-of-the-picture-id93979797&h=395065c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高比&middot;拜仁是一位歷史級的得分機器能突能投。雖然職業生涯三分命中率僅為33.5％，似乎不該列入此榜單，但不可否認得是在三分球領域，有著科比的一席之地！同時他也是單場三分球的記錄保持生涯三分球！09-10賽季，常規賽，湖人VS熱火，比賽結束前3.2秒，湖人落後2分，高比面對韋迪的防守，運球後三分線外強行出手，打板筐，在韋迪的頭頂上絕殺熱火！成為了歷史的景色。<br />\n<br />\n4.達米恩&middot;里拉德<br />\n<img src=\"https://spacecityscoop.com/wp-content/blogs.dir/178/files/2014/05/damian-lillard-chandler-parsons-nba-playoffs-houston-rockets-portland-trail-blazers1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fspacecityscoop.com%2Fwp-content%2Fblogs.dir%2F178%2Ffiles%2F2014%2F05%2Fdamian-lillard-chandler-parsons-nba-playoffs-houston-rockets-portland-trail-blazers1.jpg&h=c81558bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聽過里拉德時間了嗎?說到三分手沒可能不提里拉德，但放在這名單前列原因是他的遠射真的有一定水準，每每從不可能出手的地方出手，配合切人令人防不勝防，絕殺火箭也成為他的代表作"},{"pid":"889f4c7e83639e6e58870e1cef070da71bb141fe","tid":467366,"uid":20032,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T12:43:11.000Z","msg":"3. 賈邁爾&middot;克勞佛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nbatitlechase.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/jamal-crawford-deep-3-from-san-diego.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnbatitlechase.com%2Fblog%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F04%2Fjamal-crawford-deep-3-from-san-diego.jpg&h=cdcb1fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nwhat？他居然排第三？不過說真的，他生涯投了多少個遠程三分，我也說不清，<br />\n如果有四分線的話，他絕對是經常射四分的常客，他生涯快就完，係睇就快"},{"pid":"f3a4560c163b7abda175b7d5e558786e3088d848","tid":467366,"uid":20032,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T12:46:03.000Z","msg":"2. 史提芬居里<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://sports.cbsimg.net/images/visual/whatshot/38pointfour.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.cbsimg.net%2Fimages%2Fvisual%2Fwhatshot%2F38pointfour.png&h=edce31e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n居里絕對是籃球史上獨特的一名球員，他讓人們看到了原來三分球還能這樣投！庫裡的三分將快和準做到了極致，而且極為瘋狂，很多三分都是在行進間命中，這讓他的風格自成一派。logo shot 也是他的招牌動作,上圖也令韋少受到了生涯性的打擊"},{"pid":"b3898fdd51df4c21b8b9b86c9de541272e474da2","tid":467366,"uid":31314,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T12:49:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://stream1.gifsoup.com/view7/2670811/scholes-goal-barcelona-o.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstream1.gifsoup.com%2Fview7%2F2670811%2Fscholes-goal-barcelona-o.gif&h=7babcfb2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a36d976fa0cd955b1c0ba090662d32bb2460071e","tid":467366,"uid":20032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T12:49:21.000Z","msg":"媽咪催食飯，食埋飯打埋no.1佢"},{"pid":"4f963f31ca7517e0c5d4db2f492899e273c97729","tid":467366,"uid":13395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T12:49:37.000Z","msg":"原來講玩具<br />\n出番去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"164644e8256d06e1450322e0788594a48f6de92f","tid":467366,"uid":20032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T12:50:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://stream1.gifsoup.com/view7/2670811/scholes-goal-barcelona-o.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstream1.gifsoup.com%2Fview7%2F2670811%2Fscholes-goal-barcelona-o.gif&h=7babcfb2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n陣間會有榮譽上榜<br />\n<br />\n謝拉特係其中一個"},{"pid":"0b1e7686a5e06e3ae41d998efc6c6bfb0b89517d","tid":467366,"uid":20032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB